seo_trial_desc_first_days.comment: Description explaining that there is a trial available for a given number of days. i.e. "Free for the first 7 days"

seo_trial_desc_monthly.comment: Description explaining the recurring cost of a monthly FotMob+ subscription. i.e. "Then $4.99 / month"

seo_trial_ending_auto_renewal.comment: Used for local notification when a trial subscription is ending and auto renewing.

seo_trial_ending_expire.comment: Used for local notification when a trial subscription is ending and expiring.

seo_type_of_issue.comment: Used for title in troubleshooting mail.

seo_unattached.comment: Used to label players who are currently not signed with any team

seo_update_available.comment: Used inside parentheses behind version number - should use "mid-sentence case".

seo_view_all_plans.comment: Call to action for viewing all available subscription plans.

seo_view_full_commentary.comment: Text on button that takes you to the "Commentary" tab for a match.

seo_watch_on_tv.comment: Explaining where the user can watch the match, what TV channel or streaming service.

seo_weather_conditions.comment: Header indicating the Weather at the soccer stadium. Could be a forecast but we also show the same header after match is finished.

seo_win_probability.comment: Win probability. Short text next to the % chance of home win and away win.

seo_women.comment: Text to show in a toggle to switch between showing FIFA rankings for men and FIFA rankings for women.

seo_x_matches.comment: Used for the betting slip to show how many matches you have selected.

seo_xg_table_explanation.comment: Text for explaining what the xG table is. The text has newline seperators in it.

seo_xg_table_header.comment: A label for choosing the xG table (also called Justice table) that shows the table based on expected points.

seo_xga_short.comment: Short for expected goals against. Used in table column header so should not be longer than 4 characters.

seo_xpts_explanation.comment: Explanation of the xG table. The text has newline separators in it.

seo_xpts_explanation_green_numbers.comment: Explanation of the green numbers in the xG table. Underlying numbers refer to xG.

seo_xpts_explanation_link.comment: Link to the explanation of the xG table.

seo_xpts_explanation_red_numbers.comment: Explanation of the red numbers in the xG table. Underlying numbers refer to xG.

seo_xpts_short.comment: Short for expected points. Used in table column header so should not be longer than 4 characters.

seo_you_joined_the_league.comment: Short text in a toast dialogue explaining they succesfully joined a league through an invite link.

seo_your_subscription_has_expired.comment: Used for bottom sheet title when subscription has expired

seo_zero_points.comment: Title for "0 points medal". User gets "0 points" when they predict wrong.
